parameters:
(I'd probably disturb the performance. I should refrain from
speaking to her.)

Guardman: Break time isn't here yet. Stop slacking off and
get back to work.

Guardman: Break time isn't here yet. Stop slacking off and
get back to work.
Bartender:
Sorry to keep you waiting. Here's the drink you ordered.
Male Customer: Oh, thank you!
Male Customer: Here, let's drink together!
Bunny: Thank you You're so kind, big brother
Bunny: Well then...,
"Cheers!!"

Male Customer: Hm? What's up, you still need something?
You've got your drink, so you can go somewhere else now,
right?

Is that so. Well then, please enjoy yourself at your
leisure.
snow
But still, this is just too much!!
00_st_akane02_nomal

Akane: Hey there!! What's up? Getting angry will just chase
your luck away~ You're all dolled up for nothing~!
Hey Akane! What the hell is this about?!
00_st_akane02_nomal

Akane: What do you mean, what's this about? You said you
wanted various information, right? That's why I brought you
here.

Why must I pretend to be a waitress?! And on top of that, in
such an... embarrassing outfit!
00_st_akane02_smile

Akane: Your shyness is scoring high points considering your
usual self, but if you're aiming to please the customers,
you should straighten your back a bit more. It really suits
you after all.

Don't dodge the question. It's true that I said I wanted to
gather information about the royal capital, but...

Then we could have done so without this, by diligently
asking around in places where many people gather.
00_st_akane02_serious
Akane: Hey, calm down a bit.

Akane: If you're expecting that just by opening your mouth
the information you want will come to you, then I'll tell
you now that's not how things work in this city.

That may be true, but I'm saying there's no need to go to
such lengths...
00_st_akane02_serious
Akane: Let me continue.

Akane: With the royal capital on such high alert, the
information you can get by randomly asking around is bound
to be limited.

Akane: If you're happy being led around by slightly
embellished rumors after spending all that time, then go
ahead.

Don't suddenly start making sense! Are you trying to say
there's a necessity for this kind of behavior?!
00_st_akane02_serious

Akane: Take a deep breath and look at the faces of the
customers around us.
00_st_akane02_serious
Akane: Don't you recognize some of them?
00_st_akane02_nomal

Akane: What I'm trying to say is, this place is frequented
by people who've made their money in the royal capital.

Akane: Merchants, mercenaries, and even some officials who
work at the castle come here often. Some of them are quite
high-ranking. But I guess that's a world unknown to someone
as straight-laced as you.

Akane: If you want information that only insiders would
know, then this is the perfect place. Considering what you
want right now, I think it's worth enduring a little
discomfort for the payoff.
Akane: How about it? Am I wrong?

No, it's not "How about it? Am I wrong?" If it's not wrong,
then that makes it even worse!!

I am somewhat known in the royal capital! Just by looking
around I see several people I'm slightly acquainted with!!

If they find out I'm here! Dressed like this! Doing this
kind of thing! What am I supposed to do then?!
00_st_akane02_serious

Akane: Oh come on... This place is dimly lit and the
customers are drunk. There's no need to worry.

Akane: Besides, think about it from their perspective. Who
would imagine a knight with land holdings would be wagging
their tail in a place like this, dressed all sexy?

Wagging my tail, you say... There has to be a better way to
phrase that...

I'm at a loss for how to view this objectively, but now it
feels like I'm getting upset over something childish...
00_st_akane02_nomal

Akane: You'll get paid for gathering information, and it's
not a bad sum. Plus, it's a rare experience for you!
Opportunities like this don't come around often, you know!

Akane: Well, if you don't like it, that's fine too. It's
just that my reputation will take a little hit since I
personally recommended you

Akane, if you're just closing off my escape routes for fun,
please spare me.
00_st_akane02_nomal

Akane: When people drink down to the bottom of their glass,
they always exhale. And while they're at it, they often
spill their secrets. That's an everyday occurrence here and
nobody minds it.

Akane: Do your best. You'll be fine. I'm sure you can handle
it.

Akane: That outfit really suits you. No matter how you look
at it, you're a splendid bunny girl.
00_st_akane02_smile

Akane: Yep yep, splendid indeed, it really suits you...!
Pfft pfft pfft...
Bartender: Hey! Stop slacking off and get back to work!
00_st_akane02_nomal

Akane: Alright then, I'll leave you to it. Keep up the good
work!
You're leaving already? That's a bit sad.
00_st_akane02_nomal

Akane: Don't be so gloomy. I've got my own things to do. If
fate allows it, we'll surely meet again.

It was only for a short while, but I was completely reliant
on your help. Thank you.
00_st_akane02_smile

Akane: Make sure you calculate my commission from her sales
properly, okay?
00_st_akane02_nomal
Akane: Well then, bye-bye~
